statements: SELECT * FROM real_estate_transactions;

SELECT id, buyer_name, seller_name, property_details, transaction_amount FROM real_estate_transactions WHERE transaction_amount > 100000 ORDER BY transaction_amount DESC;

SELECT seller_name, SUM(transaction_amount) AS total_amount FROM real_estate_transactions GROUP BY seller_name HAVING total_amount > 500000 ORDER BY total_amount DESC;

SELECT buyer.name, seller.name, property.address, transaction_date FROM buyer JOIN transaction ON buyer.buyer_id = transaction.buyer_id JOIN seller ON transaction.seller_id = seller.seller_id JOIN property ON transaction.property_id = property.property_id;

SELECT buyer.name AS buyer_name, seller.name AS seller_name, property.address AS property_address, transaction.transaction_amount AS amount FROM buyer JOIN transaction ON buyer.buyer_id = transaction.buyer_id JOIN seller ON transaction.seller_id = seller.seller_id JOIN property ON transaction.property_id = property.property_id WHERE transaction.transaction_amount > 1000 ORDER BY transaction_date DESC;

SELECT buyer_name, buyer_email FROM buyer WHERE buyer_id = 1;
SELECT seller_name, property_type, property_price FROM seller INNER JOIN property ON seller.seller_id = property.property_id;
SELECT agent_name, agent_phone FROM agent WHERE agent_email LIKE '%@gmail.com';
SELECT * FROM transaction ORDER BY transaction_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM buyer ORDER BY buyer_name DESC, buyer_id LIMIT 10;
SELECT seller_name, seller_phone FROM seller WHERE seller_id IN (1, 3, 5);
SELECT property_type, AVG(property_price) AS avg_price FROM property GROUP BY property_type HAVING AVG(property_price) > 500000;

SELECT t.transaction_date, b.buyer_name, s.seller_name, p.property_address FROM transaction t JOIN buyer b ON t.buyer_id = b.buyer_id JOIN seller s ON t.seller_id = s.seller_id JOIN property p ON t.property_id = p.property_id ORDER BY t.transaction_date DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT a.agent_name, COUNT(t.transaction_id) AS total_transactions FROM agent a LEFT JOIN transaction t ON a.agent_id = t.buyer_id OR a.agent_id = t.seller_id GROUP BY a.agent_name HAVING total_transactions > 3;
